    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are doctors and stuff but it doesn't change anything. it just means more pills and more appointments and more of this. it feels like i'm just prolonging things that have already been decided. there's no dignity in just slowly fading away like this, feeling like a burden to everyone because i can't even do the simplest things anymore. it just feels so hollow.",
